content:
Hey all, I was reading the documentation over at https://www.roc-lang.org/packages/basic-cli/Stdin, and I noticed when I click on the URLs to change view I get a 404 error. I noticed that url that I'm being directed to is https://www.roc-lang.org/examples/cli/Stdin the issue is fixed when i change examples/cli to packages/basic-cli.

I would've gone and tried to fix the issue, but I don't know if this can be updated or not or where to report this. Either way I would like this issue to be known!
